  "prompt": "How do I get call history for my Airtel prepaid number?",
  "response": "To obtain the call history for your Airtel prepaid number, you can follow these steps:\n\n### 1. **Using the Airtel Thanks App:**\n   - Download and install the Airtel Thanks app from the Google Play Store or the Apple App Store if you haven't already.\n   - Log in to the app using your Airtel number.\n   - Once logged in, navigate to the section that shows your account details or usage.\n   - You should be able to find your call history there.\n\n### 2. **Via USSD Code:**\n   - Dial `*121#` or `*199#` from your Airtel prepaid number.\n   - Follow the prompts to check your call history or usage details.\n\n### 3. **SMS or Customer Care:**\n   - You can also send an SMS with the keyword for call history to the Airtel customer service number. Check the Airtel website or contact customer support for the exact keyword if you choose this method.\n   - Alternatively, you can call Airtel customer care by dialing 121 from your Airtel number and inquire about your call history.\n\n### 4. **Official Website:**\n   - Log in to the Airtel website with your mobile number.\n   - Navigate to your account or usage section to find details about your call history.\n\n### Notes:\n- The availability of these features and methods can vary by region.\n- Call history may not always be retained for long periods, so if you need specific historical data, it's best to check as soon as possible or contact customer support for assistance.\n\nIf you need further help, you can contact Airtel customer support directly.",
